vlive.english: [Lemonade victim] - Mine was... - I told you so.

vlive.korean: 진짜 거짓말 안 하고! 내가 말했지?
vlive.english: It's no lie! I told you, right?

vlive.korean: 뭐가 없다라는 거지? 내가 무슨 말 했지?
vlive.english: What are you saying isn't there? What did I say?

examples.korean: 그리 쉽지는 않을 거라고 내가 말했지.
examples.english: I told you it wouldn't be easy.

examples.korean: 거봐, 그가 올 거라고 내가 말했지.
examples.english: There, now. I told you he would come.

examples.korean: 내가 너에게 그를 과소평가하지 말라고 말했지
examples.english: I told you not to underestimate him.
I told you not to spill the milk, didn't I?

examples.korean: 그녀는 전화를 하겠다고 말했지마는 하지 않았다
examples.english: She hasn't phoned, though she said she would.
